    <DisplayName>UWP Tile Generator</DisplayName>
    <Description xml:space="preserve">Generates all the required tiles for your UWP. Simply right click on a square png or svg and select Generate UWP Tiles - within seconds you'll have all the recommended tile sizes and what's more the extension will also update your package manifest so you don't have to. This version now supports splash screen images too. This extension is designed to save time as well as adhere to the Windows 10 tile guidelines found here: http://bit.ly/1KeAfAY. For best results ensure the image has very little padding</Description>
